{
  "stem": "7860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And every railroad station had like a counter that was selling to the black marketeers food, cooked food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had lots of sort-- this cafeteria had lots of sausage-- it was a very prosperous looking railroad station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the man was very generous, giving me pieces of sausage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As I mean the pieces of sausage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a little man of small stature, a German I'm talking about, a conductor, he grabbed me and tried to call me a Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was so drunk he could walk even straight-- he was almost as tall as I was, and I wasn't tall.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as he dragged me out the door, he got entangled-- some people coming into the door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he got entangled with them and I broke away from him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was shooting at me blindly in the dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I ran back onto the platform on top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was hiding in the washroom until the train came a few minutes later and I proceeded again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a game.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a game.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I even was seen from the outside as my train used to pass by Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The stench, the smell of the burning flesh I learned later on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was so terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Coming from the from the village, from the farms, and as you come into the city, the stench of the burning ghetto in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the way, a year later, it was the Gentile uprising, the Polish Gentile uprising.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I understand 200-- some odd 1,000 Poles got killed in the Polish uprising.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mind you, the forces what they were united with the Jewish underground, I learned.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
